---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Accessibility Statement — Health Means Wealth">
  <Nav />
  <section class="prose-page">
    <h1>Accessibility statement</h1>
    <h2>Physical site</h2>
    <p>Heron Way Community Allotments is fully wheelchair accessible. Raised beds and wide pathways ensure that visitors using wheelchairs, mobility aids, or pushchairs can access and participate in all areas of the allotment.</p>
    <h2>This website</h2>
    <p>We have built this website to be as accessible as possible. This includes: semantic HTML structure, sufficient colour contrast throughout, keyboard navigation support, descriptive alt text on all images, and no auto-playing media.</p>
    <h2>Feedback</h2>
    <p>If you experience any accessibility barriers on this site, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@healthmeanswealth.org.uk">hello@healthmeanswealth.org.uk</a> and we will address the issue promptly.</p>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Base>
